| logical_plan  | Projection: cs1.product_name, cs1.store_name, cs1.store_zip, cs1.b_street_number, cs1.b_street_name, cs1.b_city, cs1.b_zip, cs1.c_street_number, cs1.c_street_name, cs1.c_city, cs1.c_zip, cs1.syear, cs1.cnt, s11, s21, s31, s12, s22, s32, cs2.syear, cs2.cnt                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |   Sort: cs1.product_name ASC NULLS LAST, cs1.store_name ASC NULLS LAST, cs2.cnt ASC NULLS LAST, cs1.s1 ASC NULLS LAST, cs2.s1 ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
