|               |                                 Projection: store_sales.ss_item_sk, store_sales.ss_wholesale_cost, store_sales.ss_list_price, store_sales.ss_coupon_amt, d1.d_year, store.s_store_name, store.s_zip, customer.c_current_addr_sk, d2.d_year, d3.d_year, hd1.hd_income_band_sk, hd2.hd_income_band_sk, ad1.ca_street_number, ad1.ca_street_name, ad1.ca_city, ad1.ca_zip                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
