|               |                                                     Projection: store_sales.ss_item_sk, store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk, store_sales.ss_addr_sk, store_sales.ss_promo_sk, store_sales.ss_wholesale_cost, store_sales.ss_list_price, store_sales.ss_coupon_amt, d1.d_year, store.s_store_name, store.s_zip, customer.c_current_cdemo_sk, customer.c_current_hdemo_sk, customer.c_current_addr_sk, d2.d_year, d3.d_year, cd1.cd_marital_status                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
